      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that gets the job done? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready to hit the road! It offers a solid, practical driving experience and is perfect for anyone seeking a reliable ride at a great value. With a bit of character and plenty of miles left to give, it\u2019s a fantastic choice for your everyday needs!",
